Maroantsetra: Andranofotsy river, Sahavary, hills east of village, swamp at headwaters of Sahafotra river. Upland swamp forest in valley bottom, cleared area nearly encroaching on the population. Population ca. 50 individuals. Collected with D.N. Cooke, A. Rakotozafy, J.H. Beach, P. P. Lowry, G. Jean
